# Marriott Bonvoy Enhanced Experience

## What We're Building
An additive web app (mobile-first) that enhances the Marriott Bonvoy experience with three hero features:
1. **Eco Rating** — per-property sustainability score (0–10) with Green Points multiplier and badges
2. **Arrival Brief** — LLM-generated personalized pre-stay briefing (weather, events, dining, transit)
3. **Pet + Local Partner Map** — pet booking integration + interactive Mapbox map of nearby services

## Hard Constraints — Never Violate These
- **Additive only** — existing Bonvoy flows must stay untouched
- **Associate Effort Delta ≤ 0** — no feature increases hotel worker workload
- **Privacy by default** — per-feature consent toggles; no PII sent to third parties without consent
- **All data is mocked** — no real Marriott API/DB connections; every mock cites its real production source
- **All generations** — do NOT frame features as "Gen Z only"; they serve all travelers

## Tech Stack
- Frontend: Next.js 14 (App Router) + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui
- Backend: FastAPI (Python 3.11)
- Maps: Mapbox GL JS
- State: Zustand
- Mock data: JSON seed files in `/data/seeds/`
- Auth: 3 hardcoded personas (Alex, Jordan, Sam) — no real auth needed

